nodes.text: Dreadnaught-Six, abbreviated to D-Six, was the sixth of six Dreadnaught-class heavy cruisers utilized in the construction of Outbound Flight.

The warship came directly from the shipyards of Rendili StarDrive for use on the project in 27 BBY. When the exploratory vessel crashed into the Redoubt and the Survivors formed a colony, the Jedi Quarantine was established there.
